-- AIDS Drug Sales Worldwide to Peak at $12 Billion in 2012, Datamonitor Says
-- Simeon Bennett
-- 2010-07-08T00:17:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/aids-drug-sales-worldwide-to-peak-at-12-billion-in-2012-datamonitor-says.html

          
          
             Global sales of HIV medicines will
peak at $12 billion in 2012, then halve by 2019 as patent
expiries increase competition from generic drugs, Datamonitor
Group said in an e-mailed statement today.  
